Package com.visionreport.core.models

package com.visionreport.core.models
  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    ChartData
    Internal model representing all dynamically generated chart data for a Vision Report.
    ChartDataItem
    Represents a single data point in a chart used within the Vision Report.
    LogModel
    Internal data model representing a single log event (step) within a test case, used by the Vision Report rendering engine.
    MediaModel
    Internal data model representing a fully processed media item (screenshot, visual artifact, or file preview) within the Vision Report.
    ReportModel
    Represents the internal data model for an entire Vision Report.
    SystemInfoModel
    Internal data model representing a system information entry for the Vision Report.
    TestModel
    Internal data model representing a single test case within a Vision Report.
